Therefore you should use:

```lang-xml
&lt;dependency&gt;
    &lt;groupId&gt;org.glassfish&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;artifactId&gt;jakarta.faces&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;version&gt;4.0.0-M1&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
```

(i.e. remove the `&lt;optional&gt;true&lt;/optional&gt;`).

